<strong>Hey — your eyes</strong>
You've been reading markdown all day. Your eyes are tired in that specific gray-on-gray way. Before you close this tab: this article isn't another wall of prose. It's shaped like the thing it's about. <strong>Don't give up</strong> — you can read more if it's HTML instead of MD. That's the whole point.
